{"tid":1937830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★戴監察手帶搭九巴269D　同車乘客大驚報警","createTime":"2020-03-22T07:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T08:51:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"00466d3f00ea4d33cc2844f68f58f7729a8bde50","tid":1937830,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4195134/org/2e77defc5ae127302a3f14567e64412b.jpg/EqjPl6rxdT50YPdhLJnQtYrRRs8Mr3lix19DxsdfQ8Y?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4195134%2Forg%2F2e77defc5ae127302a3f14567e64412b.jpg%2FEqjPl6rxdT50YPdhLJnQtYrRRs8Mr3lix19DxsdfQ8Y%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=1427ff2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日一名外籍婦人疑違反隔離令乘搭九巴269D線，同車乘客發現她右手戴着藍色監察手帶，大驚報警求助，並向司機反映。最後全車人需要在城門隧道轉車站下車，九巴職員在轉車站提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示今午12時36分接獲報案，指有戴上手帶人士出沒，事件仍在調查中。衞生署早前回覆傳媒查詢表示，截至3月19日止，共向65,943名由內地抵港人士發出檢疫令，而至今已發出超過390封警告信。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/451035/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%A4%96%E7%B1%8D%E5%A9%A6%E6%88%B4%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F%E6%89%8B%E5%B8%B6%E6%90%AD%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4269d-%E7%96%91%E9%81%95%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E4%BB%A4%E5%90%8C%E8%BB%8A%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F451035%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25B1%258D%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E6%2588%25B4%25E7%259B%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E6%2590%25AD%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4269d-%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%2595%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=674f3aa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/451035/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%A4%